text: Sybaguasu anemum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 2004. It is known from Panama.BioLib.cz - Sybaguasu anemum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2004
